latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Although there’s no day to celebrate love and it’s something we feel and do everyday, I’m totally in for a valentines date, since we don’t really get to celebrate it that way everyday, everyday is Valentine’s Day with the people you love, and here’s one day to celebrate it. 💕 Here are 4 looks for 4 different dates you’d go on; this Valentine’s Day! Single or committed; I’ve got you covered. Go out with your family, friends, partner or alone. But DO CELEBRATE IT! ❤️

latestIgtvVideos.title: Bollywood and Ethnicities! 🇮🇳
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Did this absolute amalgamation of Bollywood and the ethnicities; after all there’s only Unity in Diversity. 🇮🇳 
I’m a big time Bollywood buff so this is how I fused in both and made it into one. Half way shooting this I realised it’s a compete wacky and crazy idea; why am I even doing it? But eventually I just went with the flow! This, I will not say is my best. But it really is a lot of fun. I hope you have fun watching this as much as fun I had while filming this. Did something different, and that itself makes me content. 
Please like/comment/share; worked really hard on this one. 🌸 
.
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: “Looks for Video Call! 🌸 “
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
.
.
During this lockdown, a lot of us have been dependent on video calls; so why not dress up a bit for it too? 🙌🏻💯 Have worn the same pants cause it’s a VIDEO CALL! So chill in your pjs and wear something fun on top! Comfy, chic and stylish; all in one. 
Sajna hai mujhe sajna ke liyeee 🎵💄💃🏻 PS- Sajna is very subjective, your friends can be your sajna, your partner or you yourself can be your sajna; so please don’t hate on me asking “why only dress up for sajna?” You can dress for anybody; including for yourself! ♥️
